sequenceDiagram
    participant VLLMPod as vLLM/SGLang Pod
    participant ZMQ as ZMQ Publisher<br/>5557/TCP
    participant EventPool as KV Events Pool<br/>(Sharded Workers)
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as KV Block Index<br/>(LRU/Ristretto/Redis)
    participant Redis as Redis/Valkey<br/>6379/TCP RESP
    participant Scheduler as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(Go API)
    participant Indexer as KV-Cache Indexer<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant TokenPool as Tokenization Pool
    participant UDSTokenizer as UDS Tokenizer<br/>gRPC over UDS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over VLLMPod,Redis: Flow 1: KV-Cache Event Ingestion (Write Path)
    VLLMPod->>ZMQ: KV-cache event<br/>(BlockStored/BlockRemoved/AllBlocksCleared)
    ZMQ->>EventPool: ZMQ SUB 5557/TCP<br/>MessagePack serialized
    EventPool->>EventPool: FNV-1a shard routing<br/>(per-pod ordering)
    EventPool->>Adapter: Raw event bytes
    Adapter->>Adapter: Domain event conversion<br/>(vLLM/SGLang field mapping)
    Adapter->>Index: Add/Evict block
    Index-->>Redis: HSET/HKEYS (if Redis backend)<br/>Lua atomic operations

    Note over Scheduler,HFHub: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
    Scheduler->>Indexer: GetPodScores(prompt, model)<br/>Go API or HTTP 8080/TCP
    Indexer->>TokenPool: Tokenize request
    TokenPool->>UDSTokenizer: gRPC Tokenize<br/>/tmp/tokenizer/tokenizer-uds.socket
    UDSTokenizer->>HFHub: Download tokenizer (first call)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HFHub-->>UDSTokenizer: Tokenizer model files
    UDSTokenizer-->>TokenPool: Token IDs
    TokenPool-->>Indexer: Tokenized prompt
    Indexer->>Indexer: Compute block keys<br/>(FNV-64a hashing)
    Indexer->>Index: Lookup matching blocks
    Index-->>Redis: HKEYS lookup (if Redis)
    Redis-->>Index: Pod set for blocks
    Index-->>Indexer: Block → Pod mappings
    Indexer->>Indexer: Score pods by cache hit rate
    Indexer-->>Scheduler: map[pod]score

    Note over UDSTokenizer,HFHub: Flow 3: Tokenization Detail (UDS gRPC)
    Note right of UDSTokenizer: Runs as sidecar container<br/>Shared emptyDir volume
    Scheduler->>UDSTokenizer: RenderChatCompletion<br/>gRPC over UDS
    UDSTokenizer->>UDSTokenizer: vLLM OpenAIServingRender<br/>Chat template rendering
    UDSTokenizer->>UDSTokenizer: HuggingFace AutoTokenizer<br/>Token encoding
    UDSTokenizer-->>Scheduler: Rendered + tokenized response

    Note over Indexer,Prometheus: Metrics Export
    Prometheus->>Indexer: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    Indexer-->>Prometheus: OpenMetrics format<br/>(admissions, evictions, latency)
